void LcsReqProcessor::MolrProcessed (  BOOLEAN  remove_molr = FALSE  ) 
 

This method is invoked by the provider implementations to indicate the completion of the current MO-LR. If the 'remove_molr' flag is set to TRUE, then the MO-LR is removed from the store.
